                        <interp inst="t18490702-name-191" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN PRINDLE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a grocer of 77, Bishopsgate-street. In August last J paid the prisoner 17<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 16<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on account of Mr. Abrahams. (The prisoner received a good character.)</p>
